      "id": "PopularPost309514",
      "post_content": "Creative, I'll give it that... Also you can imprint it onto [Isochron Scepter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Isochron Scepter) to draw without worrying about splicing. Be even more ridiculous and play it with [Celestial Kirin](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Celestial Kirin) and you can destroy all lands every turn (as well as tokens since they also have a CMC of 0)",
